  "detailed_description": "You Become A Boy and Run Endlessly.<br>You have to jump over obstacles and go back when you hit a wall and find the right way.<br><br>There is nothing in both hands, and sharp thorns and dizzying cliffs stand in the way,<br>With will and quick wit, you can easily get away with it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501950/extras/eefd21f0eb3cf7292bed05cfbf20a9c5.poster.avif?t=1737976289\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501950/extras/eefd21f0eb3cf7292bed05cfbf20a9c5.webm?t=1737976289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501950/extras/eefd21f0eb3cf7292bed05cfbf20a9c5.mp4?t=1737976289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game consists of several chapters and dozens of stages contained within it.<br>The boy is constantly running forward, and you have to lead him to his destination only by jumping.<br>You can jump over obstacles or acquire keys by jumping.<br>You sometimes have to jump into the portal or get the right timing for the safe land between thorny paths.<br><br>I hope you will be a great guide to the boy's short story.",
  "about_the_game": "You Become A Boy and Run Endlessly.<br>You have to jump over obstacles and go back when you hit a wall and find the right way.<br><br>There is nothing in both hands, and sharp thorns and dizzying cliffs stand in the way,<br>With will and quick wit, you can easily get away with it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501950/extras/eefd21f0eb3cf7292bed05cfbf20a9c5.poster.avif?t=1737976289\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501950/extras/eefd21f0eb3cf7292bed05cfbf20a9c5.webm?t=1737976289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501950/extras/eefd21f0eb3cf7292bed05cfbf20a9c5.mp4?t=1737976289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game consists of several chapters and dozens of stages contained within it.<br>The boy is constantly running forward, and you have to lead him to his destination only by jumping.<br>You can jump over obstacles or acquire keys by jumping.<br>You sometimes have to jump into the portal or get the right timing for the safe land between thorny paths.<br><br>I hope you will be a great guide to the boy's short story.",
